  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      -  To determine the effect size of lumbar fusion measured by Oswestry Disability Index and
           compared with conservative treatment in patients with chronic low back pain.

        -  Meta-analysis using fixed effect model synthesis method.

        -  Included studies were retrieved from Medline and Cochrane CENTRAL databases since 1990.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
